我是只猴子
I'm a monkey.

733
01:29:21,857 --> 01:29:23,359
我很害怕
And I'm scared.

734
01:29:23,525 --> 01:29:27,905
我对大家很好  有时也会挨打
I know I have to be nice to my fellow man or I'll get a punch in the kisser.

735
01:29:28,071 --> 01:29:30,073
但我不需要上帝
I don't need a God for that.

736
01:29:30,240 --> 01:29:33,665
我们创造上帝只因为我们害怕
We created gods because we were scared.

737
01:29:33,869 --> 01:29:36,088
别再害怕  别再无知
Out of fear, out of ignorance.

738
01:29:36,246 --> 01:29:41,798
如果今天有人说闪电是神的愤怒
If someone were to say today that lightning is God expressing his anger,

739
01:29:41,960 --> 01:29:46,841
你们会怎样  我会放声大笑
what would you say? You'd laugh in their face.

740
01:29:47,007 --> 01:29:51,558
上帝不存在  上帝不存在
One more God to go. One more God to go.

741
01:29:51,761 --> 01:29:53,684
上帝不存在
One more God to go.

742
01:30:16,077 --> 01:30:21,004
我女儿梅布尔死了
My daughter, Maybelle... My little daughter died

743
