Move back, please. OK.

802
01:39:46,022 --> 01:39:48,571
肾上腺素  肾上腺素
OK. Adrenalin. Adrenalin, please.

803
01:39:49,233 --> 01:39:51,952
救活她
No way. Don't let her go.

804
01:39:52,111 --> 01:39:55,365
我不会抛弃你的  亲爱的
I'm not letting you go, sweetheart.

805
01:40:03,372 --> 01:40:04,794
救活她
Don't let her go.

806
01:40:04,957 --> 01:40:09,087
人不再团圆了  你见不到梅布尔了
The circle is broken. You won't see Maybelle again.

807
01:40:09,337 --> 01:40:10,839
退后
Stand back, please.

808
01:40:11,756 --> 01:40:14,350
三  二  一
Three, two, one.

809
01:40:19,514 --> 01:40:20,561
爱丽丝
Elise!

810
01:41:56,819 --> 01:41:58,992
我们尽力了
We've done all the tests.

811
01:42:01,365 --> 01:42:03,959
她大脑损伤太严重
She's got serious brain damage.

812
01:42:05,620 --> 01:42:11,298
我们会维持她的生命  但她已经脑死亡了
We are keeping her alive for now. But she is clinically dead.

813
01:42:14,253 --> 01:42:18,383
医疗建议是让她安静的离开
The medical team's advice is to let her go.

814
01:42:20,676 --> 01:42:22,053
