I'm sorry.

815
01:42:25,890 --> 01:42:29,019
我能见见她吗  我想见见她
Can I see her? I want to see her.

816
01:45:23,526 --> 01:45:25,028
再见  亲爱的
Goodbye, sweetheart.

817
01:45:32,284 --> 01:45:33,331
你可以…
Will you...

818
01:45:35,871 --> 01:45:39,717
如果看见梅布尔  能代我问声好吗？
Will you say hello to Maybelle for me if you see her?

